    "# NSGABLACK Framework Overview and Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "## Introduction\n",
    "\n",
    "NSGABLACK is an intelligent optimization framework based on **Biased Random Key Genetic Algorithms** that combines **Bias System**, **Surrogate Models**, and **Multiple Optimization Algorithms** to provide an efficient solution for complex optimization problems.\n",
    "\n",
    "### Core Innovations\n",
    "1. **Bias System**: Guides the search process using domain knowledge and learning information\n",
    "2. **Algorithm Integration**: Seamlessly integrates various optimization algorithms\n",
    "3. "Advanced Surrogate Models": Reduces computational cost\n",
    "\n",
    "## Framework Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "### Core Modules\n",
    "\n",
    "```\n",
    "NSGABLACK/\n",
    "├── bias/                # Bias System\n",
    "│   ├── bias_base.py   # Base class for bias system\n",
    "│   ├── bias_v2.py     # Bias system v2.0\n",
    "│   ├── bias_bayesian.py # Bayesian bias\n",
    "│   └── bias_library_algorithmic.py # Algorithmic bias library\n",
    "├── core/               # Core Components\n",
    "│   ├── solver.py      # Main solver\n",
    "│   ├── problems.py    # Problem base classes\n",
    "│   └── elite.py       # Elite management\n",
    "├── solvers/           # Optimization Algorithms\n",
    "│   ├── nsga2.py       # NSGA-II algorithm\n",
    "│   ├── moead.py       # MOEA/D algorithm\n",
    "│   ├── vns.py         # Variable Neighborhood Search\n",
    "│   ├── surrogate.py   # Surrogate model-based optimization\n",
    "│   └── monte_carlo.py # Monte Carlo methods\n",
    "├── utils/             # Utility Tools\n",
    "│   ├── parallel_evaluator.py # Parallel evaluation\n",
    "│   ├── memory_manager.py     # Memory management\n",
    "│   └── solver_extensions.py  # Solver extensions\n",
    "└── ml/               # Machine Learning Components\n",
    "    └── bayesian_optimization.py # Bayesian optimization\n",
    "```\n",
    "\n",
    "## Quick Start\n",
    "\n",
    "### Basic Usage Example"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# Import NSGABLACK framework\n",
    "from core.solver import NSGABLACKSolver\n",
    "from bias.bias_v2 import BiasSystemV2\n",
    "from utils.solver_extensions import SolverWithBias\n",
    "\n",
    "# Create a solver instance\n",
    "solver = NSGABLACKSolver(\n",
    "    problem_type=\"tsp\",  # Traveling Salesman Problem\n",
    "    algorithm=\"nsga2\",   # Use NSGA-II algorithm\n",
    "    bias_system=BiasSystemV2()  # Enable bias system\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# Solve the problem\n",
    "result = solver.optimize(\n",
    "    iterations=100,\n",
    "    population_size=100,\n",
    "    objectives=[\"minimize_distance\", \"maximize_profit\"]\n",
    ")\n",
    "\n",
    "# View results\n",
    "print(f\"Best solution: {result.best_solution}\")\n",
    "print(f\"Objective values: {result.objectives}\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
