   "source": [
    "## Key Features\n",
    "\n",
    "### 1. Bias System\n",
    "The Bias System is the core innovation of NSGABLACK, which guides the optimization process by introducing prior knowledge and learning information:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Algorithmic Bias**: Adjusts genetic operators during search\n",
    "- **Domain Knowledge Bias": Utilizes problem-specific information\n",
    "- **Adaptive Bias**: Dynamically adjusts bias strength\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2. Multi-Algorithm Integration\n",
    "NSGABLACK supports multiple optimization algorithms:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **NSGA-II**: Multi-objective genetic algorithm\n",
    "- **MOEA/D**: Decomposition-based multi-objective optimization\n",
    "- **VNS**: Variable Neighborhood Search\n",
    "- **Bayesian Optimization**: Global optimization for expensive functions\n",
    "- **Monte Carlo**: Random sampling methods\n",
    "\n",
    "### 3. Surrogate Models\n",
    "Reduce computational cost through surrogate models:\n",
    "\n",
    "- **Gaussian Process**: For expensive objective functions\n",
    "- **RBF Network**: Radial basis function interpolation\n",
    "- **Random Forest**: Tree-based ensemble model\n",
    "\n",
    "## Application Areas\n",
    "\n",
    "NSGABLACK is applicable to various optimization problems:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Combinatorial Optimization**\n",
    "   - Traveling Salesman Problem (TSP)\n",
    "   - Vehicle Routing Problem (VRP)\n",
    "   - Production Scheduling\n",
    "\n",
    "2. **Continuous Optimization**\n",
    "   - Parameter tuning\n",
    "   - Design optimization\n",
    "   - Machine learning hyperparameter optimization\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **Multi-Objective Optimization**\n",
    "   - Engineering design\n",
    "   - Investment portfolio optimization\n",
    "   - Resource allocation\n",
    "\n",
    "## Next Steps\n",
